## Description {#details}

Class storing the complete set of values that are observed by DbgValues within the current function.

Allows 2-way lookup, with <code>find</code> returning the <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#ab471937b9a227e70c7fe8bd9604014d6">Op</a> for a given <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/callingconv/#abdf8cf606905c10634e831390981b0ed">ID</a> and <code>insert</code> returning the <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/callingconv/#abdf8cf606905c10634e831390981b0ed">ID</a> for a given <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#ab471937b9a227e70c7fe8bd9604014d6">Op</a> (creating one if none exists).

Definition at line 448 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/codegen/lib/codegen/livedebugvalues/instrrefbasedimpl-h">InstrRefBasedImpl.h</a>.

### find() {#a0ff8cac5d6ff149c80d136de06314455}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>DbgOp LiveDebugValues::DbgOpIDMap::find (<a href="/docs/api/structs/livedebugvalues/dbgopid">DbgOpID</a> ID) const</>}
  labels = {["inline"]}>
Returns the <a href="/docs/api/structs/livedebugvalues/dbgop">DbgOp</a> associated with <code><a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/callingconv/#abdf8cf606905c10634e831390981b0ed">ID</a></code>.

Should only be used for IDs returned from calling <code>insert</code> from this map or <a href="/docs/api/structs/livedebugvalues/dbgopid/#a91064aebe93d3d6b7776a90451f2a854">DbgOpID::UndefID</a>.

### insert() {#a31b80daf003f8250c14e14fbb5d9a283}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>DbgOpID LiveDebugValues::DbgOpIDMap::insert (<a href="/docs/api/structs/livedebugvalues/dbgop">DbgOp</a> Op)</>}
  labels = {["inline"]}>
If <code><a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#ab471937b9a227e70c7fe8bd9604014d6">Op</a></code> does not already exist in this map, it is inserted and the corresponding <a href="/docs/api/structs/livedebugvalues/dbgopid">DbgOpID</a> is returned.

If <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#ab471937b9a227e70c7fe8bd9604014d6">Op</a> already exists in this map, then no change is made and the existing <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/callingconv/#abdf8cf606905c10634e831390981b0ed">ID</a> for <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#ab471937b9a227e70c7fe8bd9604014d6">Op</a> is returned. Calling this with the undef <a href="/docs/api/structs/livedebugvalues/dbgop">DbgOp</a> will always return <a href="/docs/api/structs/livedebugvalues/dbgopid/#a91064aebe93d3d6b7776a90451f2a854">DbgOpID::UndefID</a>.

Definition at line <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/codegen/lib/codegen/livedebugvalues/instrrefbasedimpl-h/#l00461">461</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/codegen/lib/codegen/livedebugvalues/instrrefbasedimpl-h">InstrRefBasedImpl.h</a>.
